These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, soul, electronic
1. the fan of soul is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the fan of electronic and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | cola | tea | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | reggae    | electronic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, card-games, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, musician, manager
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the manager is between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | singing    | filmmaking        | card-games |
| Job     | musician | manager | project-manager         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: rat, frog, hamster
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up     | lemonade |
| Pet        | frog  | hamster | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, house, d&b
3 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, frog
1. the fan of ambient is the owner of the snake##1
2. the fan of d&b is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | house  | d&b     | ambient |
| Pet           | mouse | frog | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, woodworking, filmmaking
3 different pets are kept: bird, snake, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | filmmaking     | photography |
| Pet     | hedgehog    | bird | snake    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, polish, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, badminton
1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the canadian and the italian##2
2. the italian is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the polish is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | italian  | polish   | canadian        |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | baseball | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, artichoke, pear
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, pakistani, french
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the russian is between the person eating pear and the pakistani##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | artichoke  | potato  | pear |
| Nationality   | pakistani | russian | french     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, thai, argentine
1. the person watching disaster movies is the argentine##1
2. the thai is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | animation  | disaster  |
| Nationality   | polish | thai | argentine |

