.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, roller
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | climbing | basketball | rugby  |
| Transport   | roller    | airplane        | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
