The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bike, roller
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the engineer##1
2. the firefighter is between the person driving the roller and the nurse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | engineer | firefighter | nurse |
| Transport   | roller     | subway    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, sprite
There 3 different types of food: radish, pomegranate, lettuce
1. the person eating lettuce is between the person drinking mirinda and the person eating radish##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | coffee      | sprite      |
| Food       | pomegranate  | lettuce | radish |

