The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, swimming
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is basketball##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | punk   | gospel   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | baseball |

