.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, american, dutch
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, badminton
1. the person who's sport is surfing is between the american and the dutch##2
2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the american is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | american | italian   | dutch   |
| Sport         | badminton  | surfing | biathlon |

