.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, sprite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, country, soul
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking sprite and the fan of country##2
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | almond-milk   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | d&b | country   |

 